title: GTA Online: Money Fronts
headline: GTA Online: Money Fronts
subtitle: Extra Lucky Wheel Spin
content:
GTA+ Members can visit The Diamond Resort & Casino to give the Lucky Wheel a second daily spin, doubling your chances to win the prize of your dreams, whether that means GTA$, RP, clothing, house chips, discount vouchers, the ever-elusive podium vehicle, or a mystery prize.

GTA+ Membership can be purchased in the Store and comes with a variety of other exclusive benefits.
